%N A396094 G.f. A(x) = B^4(x), the fourth iteration of B(x) = x/(1-x)^2.
%H A396094 Paul D. Hanna, <a href="/A396094/b396094.txt">Table of n, a(n) for n = 0..500</a>
%H A396094 <a href="/index/Rec#order_16">Index entries for linear recurrences with constant coefficients</a>, signature (30, -391, 2930, -14095, 46050, -105464, 172360, -202839, 172360, -105464, 46050, -14095, 2930, -391, 30, -1).
%F A396094 G.f. A(x) = Sum_{n>=1} a(n)*x^n satisfies the following formulas.
%F A396094 (1) A(x) = B^4(x), the fourth iteration of B(x) = x/(1-x)^2.
%F A396094 (2) A(x) = x * (1-x)^2 * (1 - 3*x + x^2)^2 * (1 - 7*x + 13*x^2 - 7*x^3 + x^4)^2 / (1 - 15*x + 83*x^2 - 220*x^3 + 303*x^4 - 220*x^5 + 83*x^6 - 15*x^7 + x^8)^2.
%F A396094 a(n) ~ c * d^n * n, where d = 6.2297364503082989942316799511876... and c = 0.041399105513218776979173347478... - _Vaclav Kotesovec_, May 19 2026
%F A396094 From _Seiichi Manyama_, May 20 2026: (Start)
%F A396094 a(n) = Sum_{i=1..n} Sum_{j=1..i} Sum_{k=1..j} k * binomial(n+i-1,2*i-1) * binomial(i+j-1,2*j-1) * binomial(j+k-1, 2*k-1,2*k-1).
%F A396094 a(n) = 30*a(n-1) - 391*a(n-2) + 2930*a(n-3) - 14095*a(n-4) + 46050*a(n-5) - 105464*a(n-6) + 172360*a(n-7) - 202839*a(n-8) + 172360*a(n-9) - 105464*a(n-10) + 46050*a(n-11) - 14095*a(n-12) + 2930*a(n-13) - 391*a(n-14) + 30*a(n-15) - a(n-16).
%F A396094 G.f.: x / ( (1-x) * (1-B(x)) * (1-B(B(x))) * (1-B(B(B(x)))) )^2, where B(x) = x/(1-x)^2. (End)
%e A396094 G.f.: A(x) = x + 8*x^2 + 60*x^3 + 436*x^4 + 3102*x^5 + 21728*x^6 + 150350*x^7 + 1030158*x^8 + 7000917*x^9 + 47251170*x^10 + ...
%e A396094 where A(x) = B^4(x), the fourth iteration of B(x) = x/(1-x)^2
%e A396094 B(x) = x + 2*x^2 + 3*x^3 + 4*x^4 + 5*x^5 + 6*x^6 + 7*x^7 + ...
%e A396094 RELATED SERIES.
%e A396094 Given B(x) = x/(1-x)^2, the g.f. of A030267 begins
%e A396094 B(B(x)) = x + 4*x^2 + 14*x^3 + 46*x^4 + 145*x^5 + 444*x^6 + 1331*x^7 + 3926*x^8 + ... + A030267(n)*x^n + ...
%e A396094 and the g.f. of A396093 begins
%e A396094 B(B(B(x))) = x + 6*x^2 + 33*x^3 + 174*x^4 + 892*x^5 + 4480*x^6 + 22149*x^7 + 108144*x^8 + ... + A396093(n)*x^n + ...
%o A396094 (PARI) {a(n) = my(A = x*(1-x)^2*(1 - 3*x + x^2)^2*(1 - 7*x + 13*x^2 - 7*x^3 + x^4)^2 / (1 - 15*x + 83*x^2 - 220*x^3 + 303*x^4 - 220*x^5 + 83*x^6 - 15*x^7 + x^8 +x*O(x^n))^2); polcoef(GF=A,n)}
%o A396094 {upto(n) = a(n); Vec(GF)}
